library("tidyr")
library("ggplot2")
reais=read.csv("~/Modelo_Covid_descargado/Data/ccaa_covid19_fallecidos.csv",header=TRUE,sep=',')
autonomias=read.csv("~/Modelo_Covid_descargado/Data/Autonomias.csv",header=TRUE,sep='\t')

d=ncol(reais)
pob=autonomias$PoblaciÃ³n
pormil=diag(1 / pob) %*% as.matrix(reais[,3:d])

reaispormil=reais
reaispormil[,3:d]=pormil



datas=seq( as.Date("2020-03-03"), by=1, len=d-2)
names(reaispormil)[-c(1,2)]=format(datas,"%Y-%m-%d")
names(reais)[-c(1,2)]=format(datas,"%Y-%m-%d")

reaislong=gather(reaispormil,key="dia",value="cantos",-cod_ine,-CCAA)
reaislong$dia=as.Date(reaislong$dia)

ggplot(reaislong) +
  geom_line(aes(dia, cantos,group=CCAA,colour=CCAA)) +
  scale_x_date() +
    theme_minimal(base_size = 14) + #tamanho da letra
  theme(
    legend.title = element_blank(),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
    legend.position = "bottom",
    plot.margin = margin(3,15,3,3,"mm")
  ) +
  coord_cartesian(clip = "off") +

  labs(x = "Date", y = "", 
       subtitle = paste("Dead people per 1000 inhabitants data given by the Spanish government"))

reaislong2=gather(reais,key="dia",value="cantos",-cod_ine,-CCAA)
reaislong2$dia=as.Date(reaislong$dia)

ggplot(reaislong2) +
  geom_line(aes(dia,cantos+1,colour=CCAA)) +
  scale_x_date() +
  scale_y_log10() +
 theme_minimal(base_size = 14) + #tamanho da letra
  theme(
    legend.title = element_blank(),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
    legend.position = "bottom",
    plot.margin = margin(3,15,3,3,"mm")
  ) + 
  labs(x = "Date", y = "", 
       subtitle = paste("log-scale dead people data given by the Spanish government"))
